				<p class=" text-slate-600">
					Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ad culpa atque beatae?
				</p>
				<Option title='Add service ' class=' bg-purple-600 my-10 py-2 group inline-flex ' iconName2='chevron'> </Option>
				</div>
				<div class="w-[70%] flex justify-end">
					<img class="size-96" src="https://img.freepik.com/vector-premium/diseno-flores-purpura-blanca-centro-purpura_1247616-832.jpg?w=826" alt="No existe">
				</div>
